以點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n甘你老母"},{"pid":"b1f9f24cf8eb2f9e68fc9cf7ab639bed15e465db","tid":25211,"uid":3078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"少既當比錢佢睇醫生<br />\n多既搵收數佬護送佢出入平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbabc3a7ac1a4a1be522aa112fc4e41ed8e0431","tid":25211,"uid":38416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/114547_fa02eecdc18be7cf91091066eddf8116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F114547_fa02eecdc18be7cf91091066eddf8116.jpg&h=cf9f98e8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真係好撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩係真唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd06c95b269ad7ddc2a15e4bae1d91919b2bf7d","tid":25211,"uid":14935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"問達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d249419ea027abf5d2caf554b5f290fa1f2e9356","tid":25211,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"做得朋友就唔應該咁小氣啦<br />\n借錢比兄弟溝女買電視何足掛齒"},{"pid":"8a3a7ad76bbc0c7d3eb43585ede6748813201018","tid":25211,"uid":23069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"我係事主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事緣係個兩條唔還錢嘅八婆係我朋友嘅朋友 唔熟 甚至可以話唔識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始因為個騙子問我有冇人要演唱會飛 (我都係受害者 我都比騙子呃錢 搵唔返個騙子)佢兩個八婆搵到我咁樣 所以我可以叫中間人 兩張飛7000 佢兩個比得4900我 我見信得過 咪借住2100佢地買飛先<br />\n之後先知原來騙子比假飛我地 個日個騙子仲同我講會退4000比我 我同左我朋友講 朋友再同唔還錢個兩條八婆講個個騙子會退4000我 所以兩個八婆之後托話同我朋友講 叫我退返2000比佢地 原因係因為:之前睇演唱會已經比人呃左幾千 依家又買到假飛 好慘 唔想到時候拎住假飛入唔到場 又知個騙子會退4000我 所以叫我退住2000佢地先 比佢地買過另一張新飛入場 咁我個陣信個騙子聽日會退4000 所以就用自己錢退比八婆先 退左2000比佢地 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但八婆明知個張飛係假嘅 仲要轉售出去比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己有錢袋入袋</span></span><br />\n依家個兩個八婆唔肯認數 話只會退2100比我 我講到話報警 佢地就屈返我轉頭話我賣假飛 仲話我去報警一齊死 佢地真係好撚on9 拎我2000仲唔還 態度串過馬撚 講到借錢唔還天經地義咁 我屌你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">btw 我係藍絲</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc251fb76c9be919e6f7e353fd19816df17f1ab1","tid":25211,"uid":23069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/114547_fa02eecdc18be7cf91091066eddf8116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F114547_fa02eecdc18be7cf91091066eddf8116.jpg&h=cf9f98e8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9bf6e454f1c9102984c41eef48fd4dd39893f6","tid":25211,"uid":23238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借錢不還真朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同班無賴唔係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644f7dbda40c4ef5d3369ad2436f9aed063e3d63","tid":25211,"uid":23238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少既當比錢佢睇醫生<br />\n多既搵收數佬護送佢出入平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌真係